Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:31.30,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:34.51,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:48.14,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}轻飘飘地随风飘扬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:52.32,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}飒爽而来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:56.14,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}若只想消磨时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:23:00.04,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}就给我认真点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:02.94,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}黑白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:07.74,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你应该也早已厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:11.60,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}被弄脏也不会放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:18.10,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}紧拥着唯一的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:20.04,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}梦想不会就此终结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:21.74,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}你依然保持本色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.84,0:23:25.93,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}随时都可以重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:30.55,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}摄人心魄的疯狂刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:33.72,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}才能拯救爱 woo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:35.86,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}决心不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:37.48,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}谁也无法破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:41.85,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}给人添麻烦又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:43.66,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}想要继续呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.77,0:23:46.05,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.18,0:23:49.30,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:54.17,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}「想要的只是时代的一页」
