Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 鞋子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我来送府上掉的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叽叽 我回来啦狒狒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 好累
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪儿被捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～命运的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喏 没鞋子回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 带我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不算近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是从这里跳出去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让她不要跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可她不听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很少有机会来女孩子的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧张心跳？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君不会去女朋友家玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有…女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀嗬～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 留下来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨也要上夜班 不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们请我果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水野 不能让姐姐太担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一位请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎 客人是头一次来我们店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要剪头发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想怎样剪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是恋爱 不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱要怎样才会顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然是「主动出击了」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主动？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主动！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然剧本还没写好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这次有吻戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吻戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吻戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吻戏～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吻戏！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}（和子妄想中）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 这次是男女的吻戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这一定会成为话题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想制造话题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戏剧就是宣传
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有看官的那一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞台才真正成为舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那角色分配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我印象中女方应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 和子大人是皆水大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…到底不能让岛上神圣的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在人前深吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:06:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果对方是拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我郑重申请候补
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欲望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻气盛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻…主动…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:15.08,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,435)\fs20\fsp1}（YoungGanGan 刊载本作漫画的杂志）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我再考虑考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流言传出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说下一部剧有吻戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真下得了手啊 沙里奈部长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手要是拓人君 须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想申请候补呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是谁 果然是和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君不会是初吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是吻 也只是演戏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:08:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素体Ayingott的复生启动准备即将就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ayingott之眼不能用第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须在使用素体本体功能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二阶段以上才能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以为了寻找巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要驾驶员人面狮乘坐电气柩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能找出下落不明的巫女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要解开日死之巫女的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的素体就能进入第三阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和Tauburn的战斗也会变得更有利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我几时可以驯化Ayingott？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能成功 就看你的欲望了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就等这一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始复出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二场庆典开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们放逐时代的时代终于到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗星
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发表困扰我一晚的吻戏角色分配
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次的吻戏是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君和水野酱的新手组合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}（拓人巴士）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园里已经引起相当大的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真加油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真加油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要加油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现鞠野～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情似乎很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我首次登台就要演吻戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜对方是谁～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叮咚 叮咚 叮咚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 感情不错的姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吻戏的女角 原来不是和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了么 令人高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作画时的你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来真的很乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塑造世界的重负与欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绘画或许就是体验神的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 这确实是段非常幸福的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画喜欢的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想画一幅你的肖像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃冰淇淋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是什么味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和鞠野一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜我选了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芒果～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起啊 次次中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着和自己这么相像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和拓人接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是种奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果这是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就必须捍卫它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我正是为此而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯化！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构成Ayingott的奥利哈康
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始光子活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是为了水野…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能输！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水野…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对要守护到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人还真少见啊 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都得一个人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学院祭上要亲嘴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您咋知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唷唷 唷…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台素体是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ayingott…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 是Ayingott
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么知道名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素体的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台素体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给人特别讨厌的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你的回归
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人切身体会到第三阶段近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ayingott之眼启动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够找出巫女藏身之所的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么只有那台素体被捏碎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许应更为慎重考虑为好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四方的…巫女们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水野…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…由我守护
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…贪食我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面狮打算一举击败银河美少年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是人面狮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Ayingott自己在发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁的心 被禁锢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是台邪恶的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不该让它复活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星剑 翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星剑 蓝宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就来救你 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豪快 银河十字斩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 和子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有接吻经历？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唷 唷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零时空间过程中 消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有日死之巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借助Ayingott的眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实看到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日死之巫女现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在于这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判明了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面狮似乎察觉了你的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公之于众其实也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像决定 不说多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即是说 Ayingott的眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机能正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有柱之印记的人降生那年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上必会有四位巫女同时降生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以认为谎言可以蒙混过关
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像以前那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 拓人果然很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么让她开口好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该已经知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她需要包庇的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩即是 日死之巫女
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.86,0:23:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:23:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和鸦之介是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近最喜欢拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印之巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.79,0:24:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐喊吧 驯化！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TVCM------------------------------------
